title: Boy, 5, found dead by canal ‘after being punished for wetting the bed had been forced to run several kilometres at night in just his pants’
text:
Opinion CHILD DEATH PROBE Boy, 5, found dead by canal ‘after being punished for wetting the bed had been forced to run several kilometres at night in just his pants’ 
The boy, known as Yanis, was discovered near a French canal in just his underwear and socks By MARYSE GODDEN
